text: I wanna sing a love song for my love, cause you are everything to me.
It is not easy to say such a thing, so I keep silent all these days.
Tell me why you never say you love me ,deliver me from endless waiting.
Somehow, you always smile without a sign. I can't think straight from day till night.
You never know I love you more than I could express it to you.
You never know I love you, I understood long before, I want to be with you.
You are mine, you are always my princess. Your princess.
I wanna always protect my true love. Snuggle up into you. Feel your heart when we hold.
Let love, never, to be end. I love you~
I love you, you are always my brave knight. Your brave knight.
I wanna always love you all my life. Snuggle up into you.
Feel your heart when we hold. Finally I feel your love as the wine.
